'''Lair''' was a [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Gender/Legends|male]], the brother-in-law of [[Benedict Vidkun]], and the brother of [[Daiv]]. He lived on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], and installed [[vermin zapper]]s such as outside [[Xizor's Palace]].

